About

Hello there!!!You can call me PK . How are you doing?

I am pursuing B.Tech (Computer Science Engineering). I am passionate about decentralisation and it's applications.I also have experience with various data transformation, ingestion tools like hive, sqoop, pig, flume and my core expertise is in Hadoop's MapReduce programming model and HDFS storage architecture . React.js , Angular.js, are the frameworks I know and use to build websites. Currently I am learning Kotlin to build android apps.

Smart Car

In this project I use On-Board-Diagnostics(OBD) and raspberry pi to send data from a car to the cloud for analysis to build a predictive .Data from the obd at real time is fed to this model to check for the theft of fuel from the vehicle.if theft takes place a notification is sent to the owner.Code for this will be uploaded soon.
